<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">We’re delighted to hear that <b>you were referred to Kingsbridge via our ‘refer a friend’ scheme</b>.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Unfortunately, <b>the details you provided for the referee do not match any current or previous policy holders</b> on our system. This means that you are not currently eligible for our offer.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">In order to be eligible for our RAF scheme, <b>the email address provided for the referee would need to be associated with their Kingsbridge account</b>.&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">We suggest that you <b>check this email address with the person that referred you</b> to Kingsbridge. Once we have this information we will be able to confirm you are eligible for this offer.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Kind regards,</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">{!User.FirstName}</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Customer Service Team</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">T: 01242 808 740</font></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>